(Her name is WILDfire. Like the fast moving fire.)



Wildfire:





Wildfire backed away from Stingtra and tilted her head. Who am I? she repeated. I am Wildfire. She imaged the quieter scene of a burning forest in the distance, with smoke in the sky.

Did they leave you? she asked Stingtra, wondering why she was lying on the ground.


