Wildfire:








Wildfire trotted through the forest, lost from the wild minds that went along the battlefield a while ago. She had been ready for battle before it started, but when it began, was was burried beneath the thoughts from the others that blanketed her own and her actions. 


She slowed and walked. She came across a familiar bot lying on the ground. It was Stingtra. She walked up to her and nudged her with her muzzle.


Wake, she said to her. 





